data.title: Dr Browns Options Baby Bottle - Reviews - What Moms Say Testimonial
data.description:
Introducing Dr. Brown’s Options baby bottle: The market’s first convertible bottle that can be used with or without the vent system. The new vent system is designed to grow with baby, and we recommend using this system to experience all the health benefits of our bottle. It helps reduce feeding problems, helps digestion and helps preserve vitamins. Some moms and dads find removing the vent a convenient option as their baby's feeding becomes more developed. The nipple venting creates a paced flow, and provides a feeding experience similar to most nipple-vented bottles. Options bottles fit most breast pumps, and are BPA-free and made in the USA. 

With the vent, benefits include:
• Helps reduce feeding problems – Our bottles are known for reducing colic, spit-up, burping and gas
• Proven to help preserve bottle milk nutrients – Vitamins C, A, and E are critical for health in infancy
• Vacuum-free feeding helps digestion – Good digestion is essential for babies, particularly newborns
• Fully-vented bottle design – Closest to breastfeeding
• Internal Vent System and silicone nipple work together – Controlled flow so babies feed at their own pace

Some parents find removing the vent a convenient option when they:
• Have a baby whose feeding becomes more developed
• Want the convenience of a nipple-vented bottle


The Power Of Choice
This innovative bottle effectively and efficiently covers all parents’ needs. Dr. Brown’s Options grows with the needs of your baby and offers healthy benefits whether your little one is experiencing feeding challenges or not. Options gives you the power of choice.

Happy feeding.

data.title: Dr Browns Natural Flow Bottles - Reviews - What Moms Say Testimonial
data.description:
Dr. Brown's Natural Flow bottles reviewed by the people who know them best - moms. See what these moms have to say about Dr. Brown's bottles and how they have helped their babies. 

At Dr. Brown’s, our focus has always been to create innovative feeding products to promote good health and optimal nutrition for baby.

Dr. Brown’s Natural Flow is the only baby bottle to feature an internal vent system that: helps preserve vitamins C, A, & E by minimizing oxidation of breastmilk and formula (read the nutrient study now); provides positive-pressure vacuum-free feeding similar to breastfeeding; and helps reduce colic, spit-up, burping and gas by eliminating negative pressure and air bubbles.

Dr. Brown’s Natural Flow baby bottles are BPA-free and have received numerous design awards and acclaim from the medical community. In fact, many of our bottles go to hospitals, NICUs, and doctor offices. Most important, moms are talking and they’re sharing with excitement the improved feeding habits of their babies.

Happy feeding.

data.title: Dr. Brown's - Happy Feeding™
data.description:
It begins the moment you find out...

Unforgettable adventures lie ahead.

In the beginning your little one will keep you on a lively schedule.

Every day, you learn more about one another...trying your best to remember each and every moment.

Sure…some days can be more interesting than others…but you wouldn’t have it any other way. 

As the seasons change and you watch them grow you will wonder where all the time went.

And more than once, you’ll catch yourself saying “Look at the miracle we made.”  

After all, there is no one like your baby. 

And at the end of each day you can rest easy knowing you’ve given them the best of everything.  

You also know, deep in your heart...the best is yet to come

Dr. Brown's
Happy feeding.

data.title: Training Cup - Dr. Brown's Soft Spout Transition Cup
data.description:
Dr. Brown's Soft Spout Transition Cup
The best way to help baby make the easy transition from bottle to cup. This “first cup” is now even better with sturdy, contoured handles that make it easier than ever for little hands to get a comfortable grip. Features a one-piece, spill-proof silicone spout valve that makes sipping easy for tiny mouths, and is also removable for easy cleaning. Attached lid stays open when baby drinks and keeps spout clean when not in use. 

• Easy to assemble and clean
• Dishwasher safe
• 6 oz/180 ml
• Recommended for babies 6 months +
• Choose from a selection of vibrant colors
